      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just grief though. grief is for something that was once there. this is different. it's like the engine was ripped out and now the car is just sitting there, useless, taking up space on the road. it's heavy. being this empty is so heavy. it feels more logical to just stop pretending then than to keep dragging this empty thing around.",
